NAME: Channel HOVER
DESC: relative value for hovering. Used in Mixer

NAME: PID ToF
DESC: output from PID controller from ToF-Sensor

NAME: ToF-SP
DESC: target distance over ground for ToF

NAME: PID Lidar
DESC: output from PID controller from LIDAR-Sensor

NAME: Lidar-SP
DESC: target distance over ground for LIDAR

NAME: ToF Raw
DESC: raw ToF value. Measurement distance over ground

NAME: Calc ToF out
DESC: calculated ToF-HOVER value. Is used to calculate CH_H

NAME: Calc Lidar out
DESC: calculated LIDAR-HOVER value. Is used to calculate CH_H
